{"tid":2509894,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人想討論下法劇？","createTime":"2021-04-29T18:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T18:45:30.000Z","uid":90460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4dc1118903ef46b375674f24c8fca43f1bb4f934","tid":2509894,"uid":90460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T18:20:37.000Z","msg":"想學法文<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知有冇人嚟討論推薦下法國劇或者法文劇<br />\n拋磚引玉講套多人講嘅<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Call My Agent! / Dix pour cent</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVDTkX7iMute9jVYnEp1zA7cjYXrNr63pMcygBLPVqHXg?filename=HqsEX4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqsEX4J.jpg&h=d5b497f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講班明星經理人嘅輕鬆喜劇，每集有一兩粒法國明星客串飾演自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />經理人喺光鮮亮麗嘅明星背後喺巴黎周圍奔波幫佢地解決問題，畀大家睇下娛樂圈幕後係咩狀態，其實明星都係普通人<br />\nNetflix有得睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/title/80133335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftitle%2F80133335&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=4acc7287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.netflix.com/title/80133335</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWhKFvN2FMEcw9ALvcBkXQdkQhTbESByzVUYVjGttUn8n?filename=OA5jdD1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOA5jdD1.jpg&h=0e6c95bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJean Reno <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQqw1s6RPCQGFAECHsmvS6cT8UC97qjfVpyaqbb1Gpa6e?filename=ObUHbq3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FObUHbq3.jpg&h=dde71a39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSigourney Weaver"},{"pid":"da90688125483c9020202d64e613b766a4695586","tid":2509894,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T18:23:14.000Z","msg":"Au service de la France<b